{{Infobox dungeon |name = Spear Pillar |image = [[File:Spear Pillar.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Spear Pillar. |tokens = 96,500 |location = Northeast of Mt. Coronet South, just below the middle of the 'mountain range' in the middle of the map. }} '''Spear Pillar''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Sinnoh]]. It has 64 tiles arranged in an 8x8 square, including 8 chest tiles, 19 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
